==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Free silver
<hw>Free silver</hw>. <def>The free coinage of silver; often, specif.,
the free coinage of silver at a fixed ratio with gold, as at the ratio
of 16 to 1, which ratio for some time represented nearly or exactly the
ratio of the market values of gold and silver respectively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

